name: Push Ups
details: This exercise is great for strengthening the chest, shoulders and the triceps

name: Dumbbell rows
details: Dumbbell rows can strengthen the back and increase muscle growth.

name: Crow Stand
details: The Crow Stand is a yoga pose that improves balance and can help build wrist, arm, and core strength.

name: Swimming
details: Swimming uses almost all the muscle groups but is a low impact exercise.

name: Triceps Dips
details: Doing triceps dips are a good way to improve your upper arms strength using only your own body weight.

name: Shoulder Stand
details: Inversion postures are great for relaxation, blood flow, and gaining a new perspective

name: Side planks
details: Side planks help build core strength, which can help reduce lower back pain.

name: Running
details: Running is a form of aerobic exercise, and it can help improve cardiovascular fitness and bone strength.

name: Lunges
details: This exercise is great for strengthening and toning the quadriceps, glutes and hamstrings.
